const Constance = {

    //Font size
    small: 16,
    medium: 18,
    semi_large: 20,
    large: 22,
    e_larger: 24,

    //Theme
    Black: "#000000",
    White: "#FFFFFF",
    Blue: "#29AAE3",
    Green: "#6DA319",
    DarkBlue: "#111224",
    Yellow: "#FECE00",
    Red: "#FD1717",
    Gold: "#FECD09",
    Grey: "#8E8E8E",
    GreyLighter: "#8A8A8A",

    //dark
    dark_background: '#2E3440',
    dark_border: '#575c66',
    dark_backgroundAlt: '#575c66',
    dark_borderAlt: '#2E3440',
    dark_text: '#ECEFF4',


    //light
    light_background: '#ededed',
    light_border: '#bdbdbd',
    light_backgroundAlt: '#eaeaeb',
    light_borderAlt: '#bdbdbd',
    light_text: '#171717'
}

export default Constance;
